
Display language settings :

edit fantasy/Game.java and change the variable 'displaylanguage',
	String displaylanguage = "english";
change the word english there to your language.
Only Dutch and English are supported for now. English is the default language
no matter how you set the displaylanguage variable.

Introduction screen:

Press Escape to skip introduction

Map keys :

arrow keys : movement on map, chooser for battle screen
x : talk to e.g. townsfolk
z : dismiss talking or ask-learn-item widget etc. go back to history of talkmode

Battle screen Keys:

x : choose action described by text e.g. attack
escape key : exit battle
arrow keys : choose enemy to attck
